  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK221">
<l>vaṟiyārkkoṉ ṟīvatē yīkaimaṟ ṟellāṅ</l>
<l> kuṟiyetirppai nīra tuṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To give to the destitute is true charity. All other gifts have the nature of (what is done for) a measured return.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
